{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":"2026-06-07T21:10:41.570Z","tool_name":"run_shell_command","tool_id":"run_shell_command__run_shell_command_1780866641567_1","parameters":{"command":"# Download GNoME paper (Scaling deep learning for materials discovery)\n# Nature paper, but often has a preprint on arXiv. Let's try to find it.\npython -c \"import arxiv; search = arxiv.Search(query='Scaling deep learning for materials discovery'); paper = next(search.results()); paper.download_pdf(dirpath='papers', filename='2023_Merchant_GNoME.pdf')\"\n\n# Download Buehler 2025 paper (Automating alloy design and discovery with physics-aware multimodal multiagent AI)\npython -c \"import arxiv; search = arxiv.Search(query='Automating alloy design and discovery with physics-aware multimodal multiagent AI'); paper = next(search.results()); paper.download_pdf(dirpath='papers', filename='2025_Buehler_Alloy_AI.pdf')\"\n\n# Download Active Learning 2025 paper\npython -c \"import arxiv; search = arxiv.Search(query='Active Learning for Conditional Inverse Design with Crystal Generation and Foundation Atomic Models'); paper = next(search.results()); paper.download_pdf(dirpath='papers', filename='2025_Li_Active_Learning_FAM.pdf')\"\n\n# Create papers/README.md\ncat > papers/README.md << 'EOF'\n# Downloaded Papers\n\n1. [Scaling deep learning for materials discovery](2023_Merchant_GNoME.pdf)\n   - Authors: Amil Merchant, Simon Batzner, et al.\n   - Year: 2023\n   - Note: GNoME paper, discovered 2.2 million crystals.\n\n2. [Automating alloy design and discovery with physics-aware multimodal multiagent AI](2025_Buehler_Alloy_AI.pdf)\n   - Authors: Alireza Ghafarollahi, Markus J. Buehler\n   - Year: 2025\n   - Note: Multiagent AI for alloy design.\n\n3. [Active Learning for Conditional Inverse Design with Crystal Generation and Foundation Atomic Models](2025_Li_Active_Learning_FAM.pdf)\n   - Authors: Zhuoyuan Li, et al.\n   - Year: 2025\n   - Note: Integration of crystal generation and foundation atomic models.\nEOF\n","description":"Download key papers using arXiv API and create README.md."}}
